               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝsār “Synaxarion” for the first half of the year (fols.
                     4ra-188va)
 I-1) Maskaram (fols. 4ra-35vc)
 I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols.
                     36ra-63vc)
 I-3) Ḫǝdār (fols. 64ra-92vc)
 I-4) Tāḫśāś (fols.
                     93ra-127vc)
 I-5) Ṭǝrr (fols. 128ra-162rc l.7)
 I-6) Yakkātit (fols.
                     162ra l.8 - 188va)
 - Za-ʾaqrabku māḥleta… “The song I am offering…”
                     (concluding prayer): fol. 188va 
 The commemorative notices are followed by
                     ʿarke-hymns
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
